title: Mafia yuumi skin concept
body:
https://imgur.com/sv02iJe

I drew an idea. This is mafia yuumi. I'm imagining she could have hard lines instead of cute lines like:

I like my whiskey... with milk. 
These guys had the audacity to pet.... my stomach.

I don't know what else, I just thought the milk/whiskey comment was great so I don't know what else to add. If you have any other ideas comment lol

replies.body: >I'll do you a favor: i'm sending you to sleep with the fishes!
She looks like a Cait Sith from Bravely Default.
